snippet.textDisplay: This was an excellent video. Thank you for taking the time to make it and up load it.  I have been taking 5000iu:s of d3 for the past year. I believe I am a long hauler from covid. I didn't get better for 6 months after getting sick until I started the d, zinc and tonic water 7 day regimen then just the d3 and zinc for 6 months.
